rComments: Well, I think she is intelligent but that's all I can say about her. She is very unorganized, came to class 5 minutes late twice in a row, and thinks people are supposed to do 24 hrs. of online readings in 1 week. And when you send her emails, she responds back rudely saying to email the TA cause she's too good for answering questions. Blah...
Class is just wrong...Tests are really rough for the C student.  She is not organized at all. There are easier electives.
Her lectures suck. She moves very fast and doesn't give decent explanations of topics.
She is a very interesting person, but not very accessible or organized.
